    • JaxbHostRegistration

    • JaxbHostRegistration

      public JaxbHostRegistration(String baseUrl, String address, String nodeName, long memory, int cores, float maxLoad, boolean online, boolean maintenance)
      Constructs a new HostRegistration with the parameters provided
      Parameters:
      baseUrl - the base URL for this host
      address - the IP address for this host
      nodeName - descriptive node name for this host
      memory - the allocated memory of this host
      cores - the available cores of this host
      maxLoad - the maximum load that this host can support
      online - whether the host is online and available for service
      online - whether the host is in maintenance mode
